      "role": "client",
      "time": "2021-05-24T10:01:42",
      "utterance": "３０歳、女です。"
    },
    {
      "role": "counselor",
      "time": "2021-05-24T10:01:56",
      "utterance": "ありがとうございます。"
    },
    {
      "role": "counselor",
      "time": "2021-05-24T10:02:18",
      "utterance": "今日は、どのようなご相談でしょうか？"
